OL,3,CDad and son died after falling from
OL,4,Cbuilding they were working on
OL,6,FA father and son who were working 21
OL,7,Ffloors up on the outside of a high-
OL,8,Frise building died when the platform
OL,9,Fthey were using suddenly plummeted.
OL,11,FDavid Bottomley, 53, and his 17-year-
OL,12,Fold son Clayton, who were from
OL,13,FYorkshire, died in the accident at the
OL,14,FUnity Building on Victoria Street in
OL,15,FLiverpool city centre in May 2021.
OL,17,FA five-day inquest heard witnesses
OL,18,Fsaid they heard the platform begin to
OL,19,Fclick "like a rollercoaster" before
OL,20,Fsuddenly dropping to the seventh floor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
