OL,3,CDad and son died after falling from
OL,4,Cbuilding they were working on
OL,6,FThomas Blanchfield saw it all from a
OL,7,Fmeeting room window. He said: "There
OL,8,Fwere four to six clicks before it went
OL,9,Finto free fall."
OL,11,FIt happened around 3:30pm on 19 May,
OL,12,Fand the inquest was told the
OL,13,Fplatform's brakes had failed.
