OL,3,CDad and son died after falling from
OL,4,Cbuilding they were working on
OL,6,FPaul Shah, a project manager for site
OL,7,Foperators Laing O'Rourke, said the
OL,8,Fplatforms had been in use for at least
OL,9,Ffive years at the time of the fatal
OL,10,Fincident, and were checked every day.
OL,12,FHe said: "The daily check is mainly a
OL,13,Fvisual, overall look at the machine.
OL,14,FThe one check we did was the function
OL,15,Fcheck, up and down, and the emergency
OL,16,Frelease."
