OL,3,CDad and son died after falling from
OL,4,Cbuilding they were working on
OL,6,FHowever, there was supposed to be
OL,7,Fanother daily brake test which staff
OL,8,Fhad not been informed about, as they
OL,9,Fhad not been given a manual, the
OL,10,Finquest heard.
OL,12,FBoth David and Clayton were seriously
OL,13,Finjured in the fall, and the dad was
OL,14,Fpronounced dead at the scene, with his
OL,15,Fcause of death being "massive blunt
OL,16,Fforce chest injuries".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
