OL,4,Cbuilding they were working on
OL,6,FClayton had been working onsite for
OL,7,Fsix months as he completed an
OL,8,Fapprenticeship with his dad's company.
OL,10,FA jury reached a conclusion of
OL,11,Faccidental death. Coroner Johanna
OL,12,FThompson said: "A daily and weekly
OL,13,Fcheck was completed as per the
OL,14,Fprovided checklist on the day/week of
OL,15,Fthe incident.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
